         <abstract id="aspace_0fa4b8d389a70dd59b0cec846ac4b33d">The materials consist of audiotapes of panel discussions, plenary sessions, public lectures, and working seminars of the International Conference on Gnosticism held at Yale in 1978 and in Springfield, Missouri, in 1983.</abstract>
